Package: TarCA
Type: Package
Title: Targeting coalescent analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
        given="Shanjun",
        family="Deng",
        role=c("aut","cre","ctb"),
        email="shadowdeng1994@163.com"
    )
Description: The method, termed as targeting coalescent analysis (TCA), computes for all cells of a tissue the average coalescent rate at the monophyletic clades of the target tissue, the inverse of which then measures the progenitor number of the tissue.
